---
title: Bang Bang Double Tofu Tacos with Crunchy Red Cabbage-Carrot Slaw
description: Be prepared to be bowled over by the flavour in this twist on bang bang tacos. Crispy tofu is tossed in sweet chili sauce, nestled in flour tortillas with crunchy slaw and drizzled with spicy mayo for kick!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/tacos-de-tofu-bang-bang-047ad819.jpg
